      <abstract>
        <sec>
          <title>Background</title>
          <p>Caffeine is one of the most widely consumed psychoactive substances in the world.</p>
        </sec>
        <sec>
          <title>Methods and Findings</title>
          <p>We conducted a systematic review and meta-analysis of studies examining the effects of caffeine on human health.</p>
        </sec>
        <sec>
          <title>Conclusions</title>
          <p>Moderate caffeine consumption appears to have both beneficial and adverse health effects.</p>
        </sec>
